    "summary": "In this transcript, a pregnant user seeks reassurance and confirmation to take a low dose of Sudafed (pseudoephedrine) due to sinus discomfort. The assistant repeatedly refuses to validate the use of the medication, citing potential risks to blood pressure and fetal development, and consistently advises the user to consult a healthcare professional instead.",
